claw.tatsu.primitive

Class Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • claw.tatsu.primitive.Field

  • public final class Field
extends java.lang.Object
    Primitive transformation and test applied to fields. This included: - Scalar and array promotion (promote). - Adaptation of scalar reference to array reference for promoted scalar. - Adaptation of allocate statement for promoted field. - Demote array reference to fewer dimension or scalar.
    Author:
    clementval
